3
00:00:44,720 --> 00:00:47,640
=Episode 18=

4
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:50,120
Back when we broke up,

5
00:00:50,120 --> 00:00:52,280
was it really just because
you changed your identity?

6
00:00:55,560 --> 00:00:56,160
Yeah.

7
00:00:58,200 --> 00:00:59,280
Well,

8
00:00:59,280 --> 00:01:01,520
wasn't anything else that happened?

9
00:01:02,720 --> 00:01:03,880
Or,

10
00:01:04,320 --> 00:01:06,520
was there someone else?

11
00:01:09,360 --> 00:01:11,400
Are you saying there was a third party?

12
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,720
I swear,

13
00:01:12,720 --> 00:01:14,960
from start to finish,
you were the only girl I loved.

14
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:15,960
Even after we broke up,

15
00:01:15,960 --> 00:01:16,960
I never got involved with anyone else.

16
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:17,800
Alright.

17
00:01:19,560 --> 00:01:20,520
That's my fault.

18
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,640
I shouldn't keep bringing up the past.

19
00:01:24,880 --> 00:01:26,400
We should look forward.

20
00:01:27,800 --> 00:01:28,520
By the way,

21
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:29,840
I booked

22
00:01:29,840 --> 00:01:31,760
