near the tea garden.

23
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:33,840
What's so special about it?

24
00:01:35,080 --> 00:01:36,160
You'll find out tomorrow.

25
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,040
Hurry up, Qin Yu.

26
00:01:51,640 --> 00:01:52,920
This place feels amazing.

27
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,280
I don't even want to leave.

28
00:01:55,160 --> 00:01:56,280
What about the gallery?

29
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,440
Forget it.

30
00:01:59,360 --> 00:02:00,200
Forget it?

31
00:02:00,600 --> 00:02:01,400
Forget it.

32
