♪I'm with you♪

33
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:09,640
♪Come with me♪

34
00:02:10,320 --> 00:02:15,320
♪Take me to the new season♪

35
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,920
♪I'm with you♪

36
00:02:18,400 --> 00:02:20,760
♪Take me please♪

37
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:26,600
♪Take me to the new season♪

38
00:02:27,000 --> 00:02:29,400
♪I'm with you♪

39
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:32,440
♪Take me please♪

40
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:38,360
♪Take me to the new season♪

41
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:43,640
I heard the hotel here is really unique.

42
00:02:43,840 --> 00:02:45,600
It's supposed to be like
an underground bunker.

43
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,200
It's gotta be romantic.

44
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,480
A bunker?

45
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:50,800
Romantic?

46
00:02:52,080 --> 00:02:52,880
You sure about that?

47
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:54,880
What would you know?

48
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,880
Sorry.

49
00:03:06,880 --> 00:03:07,600
I'm so sorry.

50
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,360
My apologies.

51
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,000
Are you okay?

52
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:24,760
Are you okay?

53
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,320
Thank you.

54
00:03:35,760 --> 00:03:36,600
Do you

55
00:03:37,040 --> 00:03:38,680
know Qiao Xiaomi?

56
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:40,760
Mr. Qin,

57
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,160
do you really not remember me?

58
00:03:44,320 --> 00:03:45,560
Do we know each other?

59
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,560
I don't understand.

60
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:49,040
After what happened,

61
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:51,160
why would you still stay with her?

62
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,000
What happened?

63
00:03:56,240 --> 00:03:56,960
Qin Yu.

64
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,440
I never thought
you were this kind of person.

65
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:00,000
You got first place so many times.

66
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,080
I only won once,

67
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,080
and you couldn't handle it?

68
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:04,040
Xiaomi, what's wrong?

69
00:04:04,040 --> 00:04:04,440
Do you even know

70
