people are saying

71
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,840
that painting was actually
drawn by you for me?

72
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,120
No.

73
00:04:08,120 --> 00:04:09,080
How... how is that possible?

74
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:09,880
Why would I?

75
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:10,640
Stop pretending.

76
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:11,560
You're the only one who knew.

77
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,520
If it wasn't you, then who was it?

78
00:04:12,520 --> 00:04:13,840
I-I'm really not pretending.

79
00:04:13,840 --> 00:04:14,760
Xiaomi, you don't understand.

80
00:04:14,760 --> 00:04:15,680
Get on your knees!

81
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:18,640
I...

82
00:04:18,920 --> 00:04:20,480
You're such a turnoff.

83
00:04:21,280 --> 00:04:22,640
You're always so weak.

84
00:04:22,640 --> 00:04:23,440
Every time someone
tells you to kneel, you do it.

85
00:04:23,440 --> 00:04:25,000
If I told you to die,
would you do that too?

86
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:29,840
Fine.

87
00:04:30,320 --> 00:04:30,960
I'll die.

88
00:04:30,960 --> 00:04:32,000
Fine, I'll do it.

89
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:33,840
Die then.

90
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,080
Do you dare?

91
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,640
You don't have the guts.

92
00:04:40,640 --> 00:04:42,080
You're not even a man.

93
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:48,560
Go away!

94
00:04:48,560 --> 00:04:49,960
I swear,
I'll file a complaint against you.

95
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:54,160
I don't remember
what you're talking about.

96
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:57,320
Tell me,

97
00:04:57,320 --> 00:04:58,520
is it possible that so many guests

98
00:04:58,520 --> 00:05:00,520
come and go through this tea garden,

99
00:05:00,520 --> 00:05:01,640
that you've mistaken me
for someone else?

100
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,200
There's no way I got it wrong.

101
00:05:03,600 --> 00:05:04,600
Because back then,

102
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:06,120
