to kill Ye Xiaoduo.

103
00:05:10,960 --> 00:05:12,280
You know Ye Xiaoduo?

104
00:05:13,760 --> 00:05:15,680
Her mother and my mother
were close friends.

105
00:05:16,240 --> 00:05:17,960
When her mother was still alive,

106
00:05:17,960 --> 00:05:19,400
they used to come
to my tea garden all the time.

107
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,400
After her mother passed away,

108
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,360
I hadn't seen Xiaoduo
for a long time either.

109
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,080
Until her birthday

110
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:27,160
that year.

111
00:05:33,640 --> 00:05:34,880
Today's my birthday.

112
00:05:35,280 --> 00:05:36,360
I don't want to waste words with you.

113
00:05:40,040 --> 00:05:41,480
Wearing a fake,

114
00:05:42,240 --> 00:05:43,400
who are you trying to impress?

115
00:05:45,920 --> 00:05:48,360
Dad bought this for my birthday.

116
00:05:49,840 --> 00:05:51,320
Why don't you ask him

117
00:05:51,320 --> 00:05:52,800
whether it's fake or not?

118
00:05:57,520 --> 00:05:58,840
You little b*stard.

119
00:05:59,960 --> 00:06:01,080
You've got some nerve talking back now?

120
00:06:01,600 --> 00:06:03,160
I don't even live in your house anymore.

121
00:06:03,520 --> 00:06:05,960
Stop polluting my ears
with that filthy mouth of yours.

122
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,840
What did you say?

123
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:15,640
Stop polluting my ears
with that filthy mouth of yours.

124
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,760
Ye Xiaoduo, just you wait!

125
00:06:26,840 --> 00:06:28,120
I'm going to kill you.

126
00:07:42,640 --> 00:07:43,400
You...

127
00:07:49,120 --> 00:07:50,600
Where did you go just now?

128
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:55,280
I noticed that waitress

129
00:07:55,280 --> 00:07:56,520
seemed a little off.

130
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:58,240
So I went to see what was going on.

131
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,720
What happened?

132
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,760
Nothing.

133
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:06,040
She probably mistook me
for someone else.

134
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:17,560
Have we

135
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,520
been here before?

136
00:08:24,040 --> 00:08:26,600
We've been to plenty of places before.

137
00:08:27,640 --> 00:08:28,440
As for this place,

138
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,200
I honestly don't remember it.

139
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:37,680
Did something come back to you?

140
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:56,400
Do you feel like

141
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:57,960
