staying at this hotel?

142
00:08:59,320 --> 00:09:00,400
If not, we can switch to another one.

143
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:07,680
It's fine.

144
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:27,920
Did we

145
00:09:32,360 --> 00:09:35,200
