149
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,680
No.

150
00:10:07,280 --> 00:10:09,000
You were the kindest,

151
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,520
sweetest girl in the world.

152
00:11:08,173 --> 00:11:10,243
♪We say good morning, we say good night♪

153
00:11:10,243 --> 00:11:13,663
♪We say we miss each other,
but never speak of the hurt♪

154
00:11:15,263 --> 00:11:17,153
♪The sweeter it is, the luckier we seem♪

155
00:11:17,153 --> 00:11:21,143
♪Yet the more romantic,
the rougher the road♪

156
00:11:22,383 --> 00:11:24,243
♪Let me go, set me free♪

157
00:11:24,243 --> 00:11:28,283
