158
00:11:28,823 --> 00:11:34,233
♪We were perfect for each other,
yet you never admitted it♪

159
00:11:35,583 --> 00:11:37,723
♪The freedom you gave me♪

160
00:11:37,723 --> 00:11:41,363
♪Became the heaviest chain I bear♪

161
00:11:42,623 --> 00:11:44,893
♪Love can barely move forward♪

162
00:11:44,893 --> 00:11:48,673
♪Yet the words still linger unspoken♪

163
00:11:49,773 --> 00:11:52,013
♪The closeness I long for♪

164
00:11:52,013 --> 00:11:56,403
♪There's no need for you
to keep avoiding it♪

165
00:11:56,813 --> 00:11:58,633
♪I don't want to break free♪

166
00:11:58,633 --> 00:12:04,003
